name: Hypnosis | Blank Eyes | Anzu | Bonnie | Hinaichi
description:
Since I'm a huge fan of hypnosis I combined 3 characters that were under mind control in their respective series: Bonnie, Tea and Hinaichi (ユリーカ, 杏, ヒナイチ )
Model is capable of generating all 3 girls and more. It also works well with other loras and inpainting.

For more of my stuff visit here: https://twitter.com/Qiller_Arts

Yes, you can also do NSFW stuff

I trained and tested it on: YuzuLemonChaiLatte_v3.5

For Bonnie (ユリーカ) I recomand adding ilol (written backwards) in prompts for more accurate results.

Keep in mind that this model was trained on 3 specific girls so it might tend to generate images similar to one of them.

Model was trained on 300 images for 1 hours.

modelVersions.name: v1
modelVersions.description:
First version, not tested that much.
I made a typo in mazaki_anzu_ so you should include that underscore at the end.
